Author: TonyL#3577
Content:
Maybe you will need re-sync from scratch. For it just delete blockchain which you have now: 
```rm -rf ~/.komodo/ROGUE/blocks
rm -rf ~/.komodo/ROGUE/chainstate
rm -rf ~/.komodo/ROGUE/database```
And start daemon again
